在第一时间进行就医的话，得到了后期可能就会变严重，也有可能变得无药可医。</p>\n<p>其实很害怕这种事情的发生，作为子女的有什么办法能够改变父母的这种根深蒂固的想法，或者有哪些力所能及的事可以去做？</p>\n","last_modified":1683684734,"replies":31,"id":938795},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_large.png?m=1644885960","name":"car","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_normal.png?m=1644885960","title":"汽车","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/car","topics":1583,"footer":"","header":"关于买车、开车及汽车文化的技术讨论","title_alternative":"Car","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960","stars":1521,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":176,"parent_node_name":"life"},"member":{"id":59091,"username":"klo424","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/klo424","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/13d9/41b7/59091_mini.png?m=1646267791","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/13d9/41b7/59091_normal.png?m=1646267791","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/13d9/41b7/59091_large.png?m=1646267791","created":1395889389,"last_modified":1646267791},"last_reply_by":"ViolaH","last_touched":1683685090,"title":"后视镜总是被贴小粘贴，怎么办？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/938755","created":1683677334,"deleted":0,"content":"几乎天天贴，车上有了也会贴，有啥招呢？\r\n\r\n![Imgur]( https://i.imgur.com/PjiOcU5.jpg)\r\n\r\n![Imgur]( https://i.imgur.com/tLEEcvR.jpg)","content_rendered":"<p>几乎天天贴，车上有了也会贴，有啥招呢？</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Imgur\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PjiOcU5.jpg\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"Imgur\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tLEEcvR.jpg\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1683677334,"replies":31,"id":938755},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1682440993","name":"career","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.pn